00:01:11,140 --> 00:01:13,940
Hiroshima, Miyajima Gourmet Tour!"

24
00:01:13,940 --> 00:01:16,040
Be sure to tune in!

25
00:01:16,040 --> 00:01:17,740
Cut!

26
00:01:17,740 --> 00:01:19,240
