Hey, get a hold of yourself!

44
00:01:58,840 --> 00:02:01,740
-Are you all right? -Mr. Kitamura?

45
00:02:23,740 --> 00:02:25,540
Brooding over passing seasons

46
00:02:25,540 --> 00:02:27,340
