47
00:02:27,340 --> 00:02:29,240
The seven wonder of Hiroshima/Miyajima.

48
00:02:29,240 --> 00:02:31,540
A mysterious case takes place within a realistic landscape.

49
00:02:31,540 --> 00:02:33,140
He sees through the one and only truth.

50
