Hi, Ran!

56
00:04:09,846 --> 00:04:11,846
What's the matter, Sonoko?

57
00:04:11,846 --> 00:04:14,446
You said that you were going to join us here and yet...

58
00:04:14,446 --> 00:04:16,446
I mean, are you still at home?

59
00:04:16,446 --> 00:04:18,446
Well, you see,

60
00:04:18,446 --> 00:04:20,946
I can't decide on what clothes to wear.

61
00:04:20,946 --> 00:04:21,946
I wonder if I should wear

62
00:04:21,946 --> 00:04:23,946
