67
00:04:38,346 --> 00:04:40,246
Sorry to keep you waiting!

68
00:04:41,546 --> 00:04:44,046
How is Mr. Kitamura?

69
00:04:44,046 --> 00:04:47,046
We're sorry to have caused you worry.

70
00:04:47,046 --> 00:04:50,046
We got him to take some medicine for now,

71
00:04:50,046 --> 00:04:53,546
