72
00:04:53,546 --> 00:04:56,646
Let's continue filming!

73
00:04:56,646 --> 00:04:58,346
All right.

74
00:04:58,346 --> 00:05:00,946
What's up, Ran?

75
00:05:00,946 --> 00:05:04,046
I guess we're leaving soon, so I'd better hang up.

76
00:05:04,046 --> 00:05:06,046
Hurry over, okay?

77
00:05:06,046 --> 00:05:07,746
Yep, okay!

78
00:05:07,746 --> 00:05:10,646
"JR Sanyo Main Line"

79
00:05:11,346 --> 00:05:15,546
My, the work of a producer sure isn't easy, is it?

80
