00:05:40,646 --> 00:05:42,646
to the destination station that is the so-called

90
00:05:42,646 --> 00:05:45,546
entrance of Miyajima, Miyajimaguchi Station.

91
00:05:45,546 --> 00:05:47,846
A few minutes' walk from the station,

92
00:05:47,846 --> 00:05:49,946
and after you pass the conger eels over rice and maple buns shops,

93
00:05:49,946 --> 00:05:52,046
the specialty of this area,

94
00:05:52,046 --> 00:05:55,446
you'll arrive at the place to board the ferry, Miyajimaguchi Pier.

95
00:05:56,846 --> 00:06:00,746
"Miyajima" -It takes about 10 minutes by ferry to Miyajima

96
00:06:00,746 --> 00:06:02,846
where the national treasure, Ikutsukushima Shrine is.

97
00:06:03,846 --> 00:06:05,046
There it is!

98
00:06:05,046 --> 00:06:08,246
"National Treasure Itsukushima Shrine"

99
00:06:09,746 --> 00:06:12,846
Since Miyajima itself is awed by many

100
00:06:12,846 --> 00:06:14,546
because of its many gods on land,

101
